rn and raised in New York City. He is a graduate of the Guildhall School of Music and Drama in London. In 2010, Schnetzer appeared in an episode of Law & Order and co-starred on the series Happy Town. He played Max Vandenburg in the film adaptation of The Book Thief (2013).","name":"Ben Schnetzer","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"벤 슈네처","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"本·施奈策（Ben Schnetzer）是美国演员。他是演员斯蒂芬·施奈策（Stephen Schnetzer）和南希·斯奈德（Nancy Snyder）的儿子。Schnetzer 在纽约市出生和长大。他毕业于伦敦市政厅音乐与戏剧学院。2010年，Schnetzer出现在《法律与秩序》的一集中，并共同主演了《快乐小镇》系列。他在电影《偷书贼》（2013 年）中饰演马克斯·范登堡。","name":"本·施奈策","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"ベン・シュネッツァー","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Бен Шнетцер","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Ben Schnetzer é um ator norte-americano nascido em 8 de fevereiro de 1990, em Nova York, EUA. Formado na Guildhall School of Music and Drama, em Londres, destacou-se pelo talento versátil e pela intensidade de suas interpretações.\n\nGanhou reconhecimento internacional com o filme Pride (2014), no qual interpretou Mark Ashton, papel que lhe trouxe aclamação da crítica. No mesmo ano, chamou a atenção em The Book Thief (2013), vivendo Max Vandenburg. Schnetzer também participou de Warcraft (2016), adaptação do popular game, e do drama Goat (2016), em que interpretou um jovem envolvido nos rituais violentos de uma fraternidade.\n\nNa televisão, esteve em produções como Happy Town (2010), The Truth About the Harry Quebert Affair (2018), Y: The Last Man (2021) e Three Women (2023).","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"本·施奈策（Ben Schnetzer）是美國演員。他是演員斯蒂芬·施奈策（Stephen Schnetzer）和南希·斯奈德（Nancy Snyder）的兒子。Schnetzer 在紐約市出生和長大。他畢業於倫敦市政廳音樂與戲劇學院。2010 年，Schnetzer 出現在《法律與秩序》的一集中，並共同主演了《快樂小鎮》系列。他在電影《偷書賊》（2013 年）中飾演馬克斯·範登堡。","name":"本·施奈策","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Бен Шнетцер","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1600369_credits":{"at":1774718577258,"data":{"id":1600369,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1609473,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Denny Huang","original_name":"Denny Huang","popularity":0.7031,"profile_path":"/3iHka0kuMEJmhvsGHQjUDDjX2W8.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"","credit_id":"69441980dc6ab79f36e6e9f7","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":2151541,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zhang Shasha","original_name":"Zhang Sha Sha","popularity":0.3179,"profile_path":"/ai762skwrhoSPj1V1ubBE3CCO0l.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6944198a86dc1008cf8bc995","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2931867,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Zheng Xiaoming","original_name":"Zheng Xiaoming","popularity":0.2065,"profile_path":"/zXdXSrcDFXo5A05486b2ozP5ZIW.jpg","cast_id":3,"character":"","credit_id":"694419977c63f427cf7056b2","order":2},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1365911,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"He Yongsheng","original_name":"He Yongsheng","popularity":0.5482,"profile_path":"/l8UD5sM3K2Xh15e0E76ymKDd9wd.jpg","cast_id":4,"character":"","credit_id":"694419be5b112b208336a9a7","order":3},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":2621339,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Min Zheng","original_name":"闵政","popularity":0.9178,"profile_path":